---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms of Service - Vizino AI" 
  description="Read the terms and conditions for using Vizino AI's interior design visualization platform."
>
  <section class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="legal-header">
        <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: February 9, 2026</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-content">
        <p class="intro">
          By accessing Vizino AI, you agree to these Terms, our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>, and future feature-specific terms. If you do not agree, please stop using the platform.
        </p>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>1. What We Provide</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Project-based interior design visualization powered by Nano Banana.</li>
            <li>Room photo uploads, custom materials, prompt libraries, and the "Help Me Write" assistant.</li>
            <li>Storage for generated visuals, prompts, and organization tools.</li>
            <li>Beta experiences that may evolve or be discontinued—credits are promotional.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>2. Accounts & Security</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Create an account with a valid email and password; keep credentials private.</li>
            <li>You are responsible for all activity on your account; report unauthorized access immediately.</li>
            <li>We may suspend or delete accounts that violate these Terms; unused V Points are forfeited.</li>
            <li>Before deleting, request data export—allow up to 30 days for delivery.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>3. Acceptable Use</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Use Vizino AI only for lawful interior design or personal planning.</li>
            <li>Do not upload infringing, obscene, harmful, or discriminatory content.</li>
            <li>Do not abuse the platform (spam, scraping, reverse-engineering, impersonation).</li>
            <li>Respect copyright—only upload content you own or have permission to use.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>



        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>4. Disclaimers</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>The platform is provided "as-is"—we do not guarantee uninterrupted uptime or perfect results.</li>
            <li>AI-generated visuals are for inspiration; verify materials with qualified professionals before acting.</li>
            <li>We are not liable for lost profits, data, or indirect damages.</li>
            <li>We may update the service, models, or credits at any time and without notice.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <div class="legal-footer">
          <p>Effective February 9, 2026.</p>
          <p><a href="/">Return to Home</a> | <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: var(--spacing-4xl) 0;
    background-color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .legal-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-gray-200);
  }

  .legal-header h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    color: var(--color-gray-800);
  }

  .last-updated {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .legal-content {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: var(--line-height-snug);
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    line-height: var(--line-height-snug);
    color: var(--color-gray-700);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
    padding: var(--spacing-2xl);
    background-color: var(--color-gray-50);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--brand-indigo);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .legal-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }

  .legal-section h2 {
    color: var(--brand-indigo);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--brand-indigo-light);
    font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
  }

  .legal-section h3 {
    color: var(--color-gray-800);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-2xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
  }

  .legal-section p {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    line-height: var(--line-height-snug);
    color: var(--color-gray-700);
  }

  .legal-section ul {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    padding-left: var(--spacing-2xl);
  }
  .legal-section li {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    line-height: var(--line-height-snug);
    color: var(--color-gray-700);
  }

  .legal-section strong {
    color: var(--color-gray-800);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
  }

  .legal-section a {
    color: var(--brand-indigo);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .legal-section a:hover {
    color: var(--brand-indigo-dark);
  }

  .contact-info {
    padding: var(--spacing-2xl);
    background-color: var(--color-gray-50);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    margin: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
  }

  .contact-info p {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .legal-footer {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-4xl);
    padding-top: var(--spacing-2xl);
    border-top: 2px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .legal-footer p {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
  }

  .legal-footer a {
    color: var(--brand-indigo);
    margin: 0 var(--spacing-md);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .legal-page {
      padding: var(--spacing-2xl) 0;
    }

    .legal-header {
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
    }

    .legal-section {
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
    }

    .legal-section h2 {
      font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
    }

    .legal-section h3 {
      font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    }
  }
</style>
